nds it tough to come out of the opening alive.} 10. Bd3 {Natural, but also very risky since the queen has nowhere to go now.} a6 {Black prepares ... b5 and ... Bb7 and slowly starts surrounding the white queen on d6 . Since White can't castle yet, this will probably end very badly soon.} *

